# System Architecture

## 1. Overview
- High-level description of components and their responsibilities
- ASCII/SVG diagram showing client, server, vector DB, LLM, analytics

## 2. Component Breakdown
### 2.1 Frontend (React SPA)
- Folder: `client/src`
- Key libraries: Vite, TypeScript, Shadcn/ui, Tailwind

### 2.2 Backend (Node.js API)
- Folder: `server/api`
- Express routes, middleware, SSE chat endpoint

### 2.3 Data Stores
- **Postgres** via Drizzle ORM (relational data)
- **ChromaDB** vector store (embeddings retrieval)

### 2.4 AI Integration
- Gemini Flash LLM adapter (`server/gemini.ts`)
- RAG pipeline flow

## 3. Data & Control Flows
- Sequence diagram: user quiz → API call → vector retrieval → LLM response

## 4. Scalability & Performance
- Caching strategy, rate limits, connection pooling
